IN RE Resignation of LYNCH 2018-1484 Supreme Court of Ohio. November 21, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell, Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, and DeGenaro, JJ., concur.

On application for retirement or resignation of David Marlborough Lynch, Attorney Registration No. 0006380, last known business address in Euclid, Ohio. Resignation accepted with disciplinary action pending.
